data.description: Charming Brick/Vinyl Siding Home featuring 3 Bdrm, 2 BA, Refinished Original Hardwood Flooring throughout, large Living Room, Dining Room, Tile Floors in Kitchen and Baths, Tile Shower in Primary BA, and so much more!  The AC Unit is approx. 7 months old, Metal Roof is approx. 10 Years old,, New Dishwasher, New Toilet in Primary Bath, New Water Filtration System under the Kitchen Sink, and the walls are ready for New Buyer(s) to pick the paint color.  This home has a Metal Roof and a Fenced-In Yard to enjoy.  Buyer(s) to verify sq ft, of home and acreage,  Utilities:  KUB Electric, Knox/Chapman Water, Xfinity Cable
